0. nano .bashrc
export ROS_DOMAIN_ID=12
source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
source /home/delta/colcon_ws/install/setup.bash
source /etc/turtlebot4_discovery/setup.bash

1. download dis-delta-team respository & dis_tutorial3
1.1 git clone https://github.com/giganizer/dis-delta-team.git
1.2 -> in dis-delta-team do: git checkout task1_realrobot   IMPORTANT
1.3 git clone https://github.com/vicoslab/dis_tutorial3

2. copy detect_people.py from colcon_ws/src/dis-delta-team/detect_people_no_point_cloud/
into colcon_ws/src/dis_tutorial3/scripts/   IMPORTANT

3. build everything

4. get robot ready:
4.1 git clone https://github.com/vicoslab/dis_tutorial5?tab=readme-ov-file
4.2 follow the tutorial

5. start localization, navigation and rviz:
-navigate into folder where map is saved (... colcon_ws/src/dis-delta-team/selfmade_map/) and do:
ros2 launch turtlebot4_navigation localization.launch.py map:=task1_realrobot.yaml
-ros2 launch turtlebot4_navigation nav2.launch.py
-ros2 launch turtlebot4_viz view_robot.launch.py
-set pose estimation
-try navigation in rviz

ros2 run delta_explorer delta_explorer (wait after start until NAV2 is ready. restart if it dosent work after a minute)
ros2 run dis_tutorial3 detect_people.py
-set up rviz: add people_marker and delta_nav_marker and remove all unnecessary stuff

ros2 run object_identifier object_identifier
ros2 run delta_greeter delta_greeter

start mission:
ros2 run mission_control mission_control
